  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Enigmatic and ambivalent, the Secret of the Shadow is like the force it dominates: now protecting with its mantle, now casting doubt and fear on those who enter it without precautions.<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>KNOWN SPELLS</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you choose this secret, you learn the @Compendium[world.spells-historia.KV3K5DetB9XXa3gK]{Toll The Dead} and @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.Z9p1vezIn95jw1Yw]{Eldritch Blast}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrips, and when you gain a level in the secret, you learn the corresponding spells indicated in the following table:<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips:</strong> @Compendium[world.spells-historia.KV3K5DetB9XXa3gK]{Toll The Dead}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.Z9p1vezIn95jw1Yw]{Eldritch Blast}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1st level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.A3q2gTNqG6fvNGrv]{Disguise Self}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.ccduLIvutyNqvkgv]{Unseen Servant}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2nd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.1N8dDMMgZ1h1YJ3B]{Invisibility}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.S7VbUetIfVT7B6Eq]{Darkness}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3rd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.XXUDGFELgoskdOD0]{Fear}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.j8NtLXOOJ3GAKF8I]{Protection from Energy}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.pxpb2eOB6bv4phAf]{Banishment}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.tEpDmYZNGc9f5OhJ]{Greater Invisibility}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.d9MwcXi7Il3HROXd]{Passwall}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.kSPRpeIx3w3nihrF]{Dream}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>MYSTERIES</strong></span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />@Compendium[world.profession-features.ezAqc2UmRh6Ds7M2]{Founding Mystery: Night view}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.gQbaIvxF3YY53rc6]{Major Mystery: Veil of Charm}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.odsMZ8f5lwcO5MRN]{Greater Mystery: Shadow Passes}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.kkuqcjNqphOV79YG]{Universal Mystery: Dark Shroud}</p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGIC OF THE SECRET<br /></strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you reach 3rd level in this Secret, you became able to modify the spells they can cast, adapting them to your current needs, and learns the following metamagic options.</span></p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.dx8rzL35VdXv5Alg]{Metamagic: Intensified spell}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.3459aAGgnOmf4yRd]{Metamagic: Subtle Spell}</p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
